405
00:23:05,100 --> 00:23:05,890
Lord Lu!

406
00:23:06,540 --> 00:23:07,420
Lord Lu!

407
00:23:09,900 --> 00:23:10,540
Lord Lu!

408
00:23:12,560 --> 00:23:13,310
Lord Lu!

